title: [Vornavis, Wooded Plains]
description: To the west, the woods become more dense overhead, while thinning out to the east and allowing more moonlight to shine into the forest.  Owls hoot noisily from the trees, their calls echoing in the woods in all directions.

To the west, the woods become more dense overhead, while thinning out to the east and allowing more sunlight to shine into the forest.  Birds whistle shrilly from the trees, their calls echoing in the woods in all directions.
